    "extraversion": "Your energy from social interaction is balanced; You neither strongly seek nor consistently avoid being with others.",
    "agreeableness": "You tend to be skeptical, competitive, and prioritize directness and self-interest over cooperation.",
    "neuroticism": "You are very calm, emotionally secure, and rarely feel anxious, sad, or tense."
  },
